about.title: About
about.p1: Printing Facility is a source-available research project by EPLUS+ students at Suankularb Wittayalai, developed in collaboration with the Suankularb Wittayalai Student Committee.
about.p2: If you're curious to see the magic behind this project, you're warmly invited to explore the GitHub repository.
about.p3: Printing Facility may collect data for analytics and research purposes, see our <a1>Privacy Policy</a1> and <a2>Terms of Service</a2> for more information.
